      "message": "[minor] Line 678: ЁЯЯб On API \u003c R, if `CONTROL_ZOOM_RATIO_RANGE` is not available but the device doesn\u0027t support `SCALER_AVAILABLE_MAX_DIGITAL_ZOOM` either (returns null тЖТ defaults to 1f), the code will set `CONTROL_ZOOM_RATIO` with the unclamped `ratio` value. This could crash or be ignored depending on the HAL. Consider falling through to the crop-region path when range is null on R+ devices, or at minimum clamping to 1f..maxDigitalZoom.",
