      "side": 1,
      "message": "[major] Line 746: ЁЯЯб The repeating request is submitted with `null` as the CaptureCallback, but the original session setup uses a `captureCallback` that handles codec start and key frame insertion. Replacing the repeating request with one that has a null callback means codec-start logic (e.g., `startMediaCodecIfNeeded`) won\u0027t fire if a zoom change happens before the codec is started. Consider storing and reusing the original `CaptureCallback`.",
      "revId": "43a0949874ea6086ed6b0a601e3a3ebe1dff2044",
      "serverId": "1e26b4c1-6b8c-47ff-9df7-501b633d3b5a"
