      "message": "[major] Line 844: ЁЯЯб Storing `previous` and conditionally restoring it when `IllegalStateException` is caught is a reasonable defensive measure. However, between `videoParams.cameraSession \u003d session` (line 845) and the exception at line 848, `listener.onOpened()` (line 846) is already called, which may trigger dependent logic that assumes the session is valid. Consider moving `listener.onOpened()` after the successful `setRepeatingRequest` call.",
