      "message": "[minor] Line 844: ЁЯЯб The `previous` session reference is restored on `IllegalStateException`, but if the previous session was also closed (which is likely since a new session implicitly closes the old one), the stored `cameraSession` will reference a dead session. Subsequent `setZoomRatio` calls would try to use it and also fail. Consider setting `cameraSession \u003d null` instead of `previous` on failure, or better yet, not storing the session until `setRepeatingRequest` succeeds.",
      "revId": "43a0949874ea6086ed6b0a601e3a3ebe1dff2044",
